    "description": "Jaypore International Enterprises, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Digital Marketing Manager for our Kochi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Jaypore International Enterprises:\nJaypore International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Jaypore International Enterprises!",
